column5: Don't care if it's nasty out. Me and the pups hunkered down to our breakfast of champions.  During perch season the livin is good.
I'm eating peanut butter and friggen jam....and you show me THIS!  looks great, reminds me of my weekend breakies.
I warmed up some frozen waffles in the toaster.  Pretty sure the perch would have been much nicer
Bon apetit! Simple pleasures are some of the best things in life. Good for you!
